    "Fig. 1 The number of studies used in this review based on the year of publication.",
    "This section describes the review methods used and how the existing works on DL techniques were gathered, extracted, and analyzed.",
    "Several electronic databases have been obtained from Google Scholar searches, including IEEE, Springer, ACM, and Elsevier, using the keywords \"Deep Learning\" AND \"Predict Student Performance\" AND \"Predict Student Outcome\" AND \"Predict Student at Risk\" AND \"Hybrid Model\".",
    "An extensive collection of articles was gathered and filtered; thus, 46 journal articles published between 2019 and 2023 were selected as the final set, as shown in Figure 1.",
    "All the selected articles used either one or more DL techniques or combined DL with ML techniques to predict student's academic performance in terms of achievement, completion in courses, and students at risk of failure."
